High Resolution Nude Scans4:

Images scanned from men's magazines at high resolution to include the original half-tone colour rendering. Because the half-tone rendering is intact, these images are suitable for printing to any size including life-size and wall-size posters. Image resolution may need to be reduced for accurate reproduction at small scale to avoid moire interference.
